  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1830a922-e9c0-4b92-b341-dc3a5c5d01d0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-ce1ebc24-d1f3-4483-be90-929351aa75d5\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3b3f9a16-63f0-4ad8-bf93-5df3bea887a2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">코로나로 인해 미술 전시시장도 많이 위축되고 전시회도 일정이 취소되거나 미뤄지는 등 많은 고통을 겪고 있습니다. 2023년에는 더욱 갤러리 시장이 활성화되어 전시나 기타 여러가지 홍보가 많이 이루어졌으면 하는 바램이 있습니다. 먼저 미술관계자 여러분들에게 많은 응원과 격려의 말</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-bba4e997-f98f-40c2-9849-db368327f9ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">씀을 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-121aa47f-a9e7-4d06-8b5e-8c7010b89807\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222943936522/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-608fffc2-4bd7-40fd-961a-e4e12f06408a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222943936522/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c1586ace-35cd-4e9c-9866-1eedc4243a4c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222943936522/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-13fccbce-9a3c-491f-b68f-e8e400f3488e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-11f5fd35-7667-4fac-bbaf-90c9546f1ae5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-789d0df7-b3c0-4629-a465-1d650e70f6d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-f68b5cd5-2b16-4a12-81e8-de9430f60682\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222943936522/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e9a39214-60ce-48eb-983a-c552965eda42\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f5af975b-3da0-41a4-867c-fc2b23010dec\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>3단 리플렛은 이럴때 주문하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb3e0777-c32b-4e36-b2d3-ecd40da1d437\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0e6cdb8f-3bc9-409e-a249-d0119a746306\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">3단 리플렛은 6페이지로 구성이 되어 있어서 가장 많은 내용을 담을 수 있습니다. 4단도 있지만 보톤 면적은 3단과 비슷하고 구분만 4단으로 나눠집니다. 종이의 기본 사이즈가 3단까지로의 구성이 일반적이기 때문에 3단 리플렛이 가장 많은 내용을 담을 수 있는 템플릿이라고 생각하시면 됩니다. 3단 리플렛은 접었을 때 A4나 B5로 구성되는 형식입니다. 보통 갤러리 전체의 홍보용이나 대표작가의 작품을 메인에 넣고 서브작가들의 내용을 담을 때 활용되는 템플릿입니다. 3단 리플렛은 요 근래 가격도 저렴해지고 종합 홍보용으로 많이 각광받고 있습니다. 몇년전까지만 해도 기본 500부 등 일정 수량 이상이 아니면 단가 경쟁력이 적었으나 디지털인쇄기의 발달로 인해 단가 경쟁력이 많아진 상황입니다. 많은 이용 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6ff3b1f3-b8e8-48af-a4a2-2b3f6fe66ed8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-095d624b-c7ff-4c1f-a8b5-155c1e725ede\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b3d74d61-80cd-47c5-b8b4-138e8e6e426f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-41bb3cbc-035b-4b25-be0c-d628ac5aaaee\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222943936522/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9c4f9e8b-4e23-40dc-b7d1-ea923a41f002\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-29e24365-5d6c-41b8-ac6a-9956b03a19f7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>기본 사이즈, 3단으로 접었을 때 A4/B5</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-51f5922e-1458-4b2b-8994-1b6a9ab20efb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a532ea37-e72f-4a17-9c33-c9cdc06e10f9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">3단 리플렛의 기본 사이즈는 접었을 때 A4/B5(16절)입니다. B계열의 경우 업체마다 조금씩 사이즈가 달라질 수 있으니 이점은 참고만 해주시기 바랍니다. 오버되지 않는 범위내에서 사이즈 조정은 가능합니다. 일단 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 기본 사이즈는 다음과 같습니다. 다만 사이즈는 일부 저정될 수 있습니다. 기본 사이즈에 맞게 제작이 됩니다. 또는 가장 납기가 빠르거나 수량에 따라 사이즈는 일부 조정될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a56d4fbc-ed42-4462-b5ce-e6b39f03fb61\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222943936522/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e7248922-9c68-4e90-a2f8-554d2003294d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222943936522/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-75fb3216-962f-4868-9f2e-4c3ee63ba276\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-64b53764-0e81-400b-ab9e-9842a079c8c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222943936522/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-129dd956-6f58-4e55-a8bd-d80c19e871e7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1c3a5efb-a593-4e1d-a73f-79b24c370c92\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>기본 종이, 랑데뷰 울트라화이트 240g</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b935469-83f8-41c1-b385-1851e6a12c15\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7b35ef74-6340-4872-8b0d-e16591ae5b88\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">엽서나 2단 리플렛처럼 가장 기본적인 종이를 랑데뷰로 선택했습니다. 하지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 모든 제품은 다양한 종이를 선택하실 수 있습니다. 다음은 기본적인 종이를 나열해 드립니다. 고객분들은 종이의 종류를 세심하게 이해하거나 선택하기 힘드실 수 있습니다. 기본적인 추천 종이를 선택해 주십시요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c072355-c6e8-401d-a880-b760635350cd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-45e853c2-00de-4e0c-a37c-d407293060aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-456217e3-7e8c-4f4e-a7ac-0b453492fd1f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1a2478e3-3e20-493c-82ed-97423c62e93d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">01. 랑데뷰 울트라화이트 240g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5bf38176-365b-47f9-9654-4e58f6dfa038\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e97e9d6-8012-4546-b41a-5e76bb42fe1e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">02. 랑데뷰 내추럴 240g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1fbc60d1-eb0b-4891-b39a-539e005fc91c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-00f9ac2b-e197-469d-bdee-34a52e6fcc19\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">03. 아르떼 울트라화이트 230g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0da580c3-4b35-4b69-bd21-b492bc0315fc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-53de1628-297b-4c14-ba1e-e521f6161c7e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">04. 린넨커버 솔라화이트 216g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8d04c741-175c-46d5-b6d3-aa3e9757c66e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a998a0d1-eaf3-4953-8b08-005258e3a4f1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">05. 마쉬멜로우 화이트 209g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6176efc0-6f1c-4b95-b777-563066f34a23\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-32b610f8-c331-44c9-93fd-e868aa422878\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">06. 콩코르 컨셉 블루펄 250g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-caeddf8f-f64a-4f97-b6fa-415e327a2eab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-21da7239-78f7-4095-ac11-028fedc4049b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">07. 스타드림 쿼츠 240g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c92c8bbc-fa66-4afa-9f4a-2fa4a2cbd3f7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4cb8aafb-cff3-4aa5-b8ca-44b91cdf6daf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">08. 빌리지 화이트 200g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7b616a25-e215-43b4-a1fc-3ea233157218\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0351fa0d-b2d7-403f-bdf3-d4130dc8426c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">09. 스노우지 백색 250g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9d1fe745-0e6c-4dfa-a86c-e2b9b014cb66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5d40b896-fa24-4725-899e-fe51720da5ae\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">10. 몽블랑 엑스트라화이트 240g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7b7b9827-f19d-4423-88ab-bca2bb948c50\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0db70502-048a-4697-979d-8cf1c31d67a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-01063b88-113e-4d60-aeb4-209f2c323717\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-dd69ceeb-345e-4b91-909c-e71ad8490ffa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p c